  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Dual Wielding sphere, base attack bonus +5.</p>\n<p>While in this stance, you begin to spin your main-hand and off-hand weapons rapidly in front of you. Whenever a weapon attack roll is made against you (and you are aware of it), you may attempt to disrupt the attack before it can harm you. Unusually massive weapons and attacks generated by spell effects cannot be deflected in this way.</p>\n<p>You can expend an attack of opportunity and make a melee attack roll with both your main-hand and off-hand weapons, both at your highest bonus (but suffering the penalties associated with dual attack to both attacks). If one result is greater than the attack roll total of the attack, the attack deals half damage, before applying damage reduction and similar abilities. If both results are greater than the attack, the attempted attack misses you completely.</p>\n",
